  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4904751/" class="title-link">说古道今论海权</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4904751"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/24500271/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u24500271-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/24500271/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">碧落</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-04-12"
      class="main-meta">2011-04-12 18:50:31</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4904751_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  没想到《海权论》的书评区竟然是如此的平静，实在是令人感到惊讶。 笔者也没做过这方面的调查，就是目前国内看过、哪怕是听过《海权论》的人多不？但是据笔者的经验似乎不是很多，100多年前此书诞生，也曾经引起了阵阵军事思想风暴，主要西方国家都深受此书的影响，作者关于海...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4904751/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4904751_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4904751_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
